We speak to the Canadian government and their Prime Minister; they need a touch.

00:42:57.840 --> 00:43:06.211
Lord, we thank you that you're touching Elon Musk and touching Trump.

00:43:06.212 --> 00:43:25.739
We speak to the financial outpouring. Satan, get your hands off of our money now in Jesus'name.

00:43:25.740 --> 00:44:13.557
Release the children of God's money for the great wealth transfer. There is no dam holding back the money.

00:44:13.558 --> 00:44:52.159
I heard them plotting in Russia; they don't want to be underneath the West's influence anymore.

00:44:52.160 --> 00:45:40.639
I see the BRICS nations wanting to rise up. The Beast system is rising up in the days ahead.

