00:47:47.547 --> 00:48:04.385
Just like Paul and Silas praying in the midnight hour, there was a great shaking in that jail cell.

00:48:04.386 --> 00:48:20.945
The jail cell of your circumstances is coming open today. Those chains are falling off as you worship and praise.

00:48:20.946 --> 00:52:07.809
The days of fun have just begun. We'll be back tomorrow and we'll pray again.

00:52:07.810 --> 00:52:26.785
I've got to pray more in the spirit because that's what gets the job done.

00:52:26.786 --> 00:52:44.619
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you so much.

00:52:44.620 --> 00:52:52.000
God bless you all and we'll see you again tomorrow. Bye-bye.

